### Project API Tests
### Tests for ProjectController endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080
### OpenCode server: http://localhost:4096

### List all projects
### Returns list of all available projects
GET http://localhost:8080/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get current project
### Returns the currently active project details
GET http://localhost:8080/api/projects/current
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Update current project
### Patch update for current project settings
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/projects/current
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "commands": {
    "build": "mvn clean install",
    "test": "mvn test"
  }
}

###
